node.text:
❤️Hugs for Scout❤️

Our good friend, the one and only @scoutgoldenretriever, who is famous for giving FREE HUGS, was recently diagnosed with cancer. 💔 

His family’s world has been turned upside down. The dog with a heart of gold has a tumor on his heart.

I first met Scout, and his wonderful mom, Melissa, several years ago at a Halloween costume contest. The moment we met, Scout pushed his nose into my bag and helped himself to a treat. He’s my kind of dog!! 😁
Will you join me in sending hugs to Scout? 

Thank you, @vitothedogfather for creating this sign. If you’d like a copy that you can print yourself, shoot me a DM. 

We love you, Scout! #HugsForScout

node.text:
Who rode it better? 🐴

As a child, did you ever wish for a pony? Toy ponies have come a long way since I was a kid, riding a broom stick with a horse head. 🤣

We gave our little horse-lover, Stella Rae, a @ponycycle for her 3rd birthday. She still rides it everyday - and she’ll be 5 soon. She brushes it’s mane and tail too - it’s the cutest!

We just got another PonyCycle (updated model U 2021) for all the kiddos to ride when they come over.  It’s a huge hit!

Are you thinking of a child who would love their very own PonyCycle? We asked @ponycycle if they could offer my friends a DISCOUNT and they said YES! Just click the Linktree in my bio to save 10% 

Ride on!
#ponycycle

node.text:
Rivers know this: there is no hurry. We shall get there someday. -Winnie the Pooh
***
We are taking this quote to heart as we continue to wait… and wait for the Floater (our house that floats on the river) to be repaired. Broken water pipes caused extensive damage. 8 months later we are still waiting for the repairs to be finished.
***
I know we’re not alone. Many of you have had water damage. Some of you are dealing with it right now. So to you, and to ourselves, we say…
JUST KEEP PADDLING!

node.text:
Exercise? I thought you said EXTRA FRIES.
🍟
This morning, when I heard on @livekellyandryan that today is #NationalFrenchFryDay I just had to celebrate! So we headed to @mcdonalds and got ourselves some 🍟
🎥 
Who wants to see some behind-the-scenes footage?
😋
P.S. Too many fries are not good for dogs (or people, for that matter) so please don’t let them eat fries willy nilly.

❤️🤍💙

🍉
